data.title: General Gherman Titov - Stamp(S) Signed
data.meta_description: General Gherman Titov - Stamp(S) Signed  - Item 312090. The second man to orbit Earth signs a Hungarian postage stamp created to honor his achievementStamp signed: 'Titov' 1¾x1¼. Hungarian 60 fillér stamp bearing Titov's image and a fanciful version of his space vehicle. Shop for General Gherman Titov related autographs, signed photographs, historical documents and manuscripts from the world's largest collection. Every purchase includes our industry recognized COA. Worldwide shipping available.
